description: Try our easy to follow Boiled Egg With Rainbow Soldiers recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
name: Boiled Egg With Rainbow Soldiers Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Drain eggs and asparagus. Run cold water over eggs and cut off tops. Serve eggs in egg cups with toast and rainbow vegetable soldiers for dipping.
